{"tid":2501050,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"佔中1小時　三隧道崩潰 130萬人困港島 孕婦失救","createTime":"2021-04-23T06:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:37:48.000Z","uid":7814,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"102cafba426918fb0d3af0a375ab23c6a5ac260c","tid":2501050,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U7yv-0nIaAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU7yv-0nIaAY&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzgmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=5a07811b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U7yv-0nIaAY</a><br />\n<br />\n「幫港出聲」在今年6月，委託了「顧問公司」發表研究報告，指出一旦發生佔中，將導致交通嚴重堵塞、甚至癱瘓。發言人周融形容，佔中可以「殺死」這城市，香港人應該思考，是否允許這樣的事情發生。<br />\n<br />\n「幫港出聲」同時發布了「佔領中環 can kill this city! 」為題的4分鐘短片。短片形容，中環是香港的心臟，若有人佔中，等於直插香港心臟。短片又介紹研究報告的內容，指中環一旦被佔，最快6分鐘就會塞1公里道路，1小時內可令「三條隧道崩潰，130萬人被困港島」，孕婦、緊急失救亦「絕對有可能發生」。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">最後什麼都沒有發生。</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214386ce2e99d84b5e211f44671c851e88013b82","tid":2501050,"uid":7814,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"屌你藍絲果種柒真係非筆墨可以形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dce9b452418530118cf1463f4a776c3cfa40a5","tid":2501050,"uid":268591,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"假新聞pk鄧又睇唔到"},{"pid":"4e3fc2489ae63c9bba7bd403bdc926b3dd8bdb05","tid":2501050,"uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"點會無事發生？<br />\n明明佔中搞到律敦治醫院有個孕婦生K胎<br />\n<i